STATE
v.
Craig C. WISSINK. No. 484P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 1, 2005. M. Alexander Charns, Durham, for Craig C. Wissink. Edward W. Grannis, Jr., District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st day of September 2005 by Attorney General for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Allowed pending determination of Petition for Discretionary Review by order of the Court in conference this the 1st day of September 2005."
